{"tid":1489951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯] 點解你地唔支持821塞鐵?","createTime":"2019-08-20T03:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:47:17.000Z","uid":61182,"like":17,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0a51322c5e33ef3ade6d520e0612c4d319fb142b","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"每次逢要準備塞鐵成日就會有班所謂既<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「我睇通曬全局既軍師」</span></span><br />\n出黎反塞鐵<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地班人同我擘大你個屎眼同我睇清楚，塞鐵既用處同效益你地到底有冇睇透過，有冇諗過? <br />\n一聽到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「阻住你反工」</span></span>就不斷盲反? <br />\n==============================================================<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不服來辯</span></div></span></strong></ins></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">試下諗下 岩岩7婆個記招你聽左乜撚野?!</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">遊行示威<strong>行左幾多次</strong>，前日170萬人再出黎，<strong>政府都係繼續白內障</strong>，咩都唔回應。</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>勇武前線手足<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">700個</span>比人拉左。</div><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">連機場都比人出埋禁制令，佢出得一次可以有第二次，第三次，唔係話機場冇用，而係你睇下每次要幾多人先至可以癱瘓機場，諗下個日阻人飛有幾多人屌。</strong></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n重點係，<span style=\"color: red;\">一個月前7.21冇人唔記得</span>，你同我講要幫佢地討回公道。結果你同我講，繼<span style=\"font-size: large;\">續坐啦，坐坐下政府就會開竅，會出黎回應。唔好傻啦，你唔升級都連班「真。打工仔」，商家佬都噪政府，我地邊夠籌碼去談判？</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">而唯一你唔洗驚會比人用車撞<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">比狗拉去凌虐</span>，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非既抗爭升級方式就係升級不合作運動</span></span></strong> </div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">你地班和理非仲諗住行行企企到幾時? <br />\n170萬人再再再行出黎已經打曬飛機?! <br />\n7婆有冇理過啊?!<br />\n定玩823人鏈手拖手好威威? <br />\n呢排仲要吹風話唔好再勇武?! <br />\n屌 對唔對得住比人拉左既手足啊?! </div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n由8.21開始，荔景，九龍塘，炮台山塞9死地鐵呢個命脈。再唔回應訴求，我地就塞曬全線，塞到林病怕為止。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">如果連呢種犧牲同覺悟都做唔到，香港人唔好同我出黎講抗爭。</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"11baf963170760f03a37c6479249062d69c955ab","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EocDYdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEocDYdz.jpg&h=f96406c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gr3cidz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgr3cidz.jpg&h=dd6a3e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c890d72c3b3c39ea09c1e4a668b6ec4b2a70b79","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDqVf0j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDqVf0j.jpg&h=f0b4d18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4a7kr60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4a7kr60.jpg&h=0dbf0ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gNnkr60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgNnkr60.jpg&h=63091dc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7ebf33de2dc851cb492b0b542a654f159860de8","tid":1489951,"uid":6261,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔塞機場"},{"pid":"90b69236ab613a6127dc48ab2fd0068dada78340","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Luksp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Luksp.jpg&h=4edcdb0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ea10577424562f3a30fac78