炮台山塞9死地鐵呢個命脈。再唔回應訴求，我地就塞曬全線，塞到林病怕為止。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">如果連呢種犧牲同覺悟都做唔到，香港人唔好同我出黎講抗爭。</div></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"支持, 塞撚死佢, 我唔介意每日身水身汗行路番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 住炮台山"},{"pid":"020076a32d6aeaf69102a12a663062920111503e","tid":1489951,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"塞鐵太小兒科啦"},{"pid":"b574c70813d2596640ed38c6e436b2df396c17b8","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e7ebf33de2dc851cb492b0b542a654f159860de8","tid":1489951,"uid":6261,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔塞機場"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"塞機場塞左咁多次，政府有冇回應過五大?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqMEHF1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqMEHF1.jpg&h=88c4478f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f319707c5270ebea5b265039e53c4906134a6f81","tid":1489951,"uid":61182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"020076a32d6aeaf69102a12a663062920111503e","tid":1489951,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"塞鐵太小兒科啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"請問有咩高見? <br />\n我好想知香港人和理非仲可以點升級除左全民皆兵外"},{"pid":"6454913fc9ca3d79e76a4ff97bab8a092967903d","tid":1489951,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b652a069723295f4be3c1eb7b97995a07dd6e782","tid":1489951,"uid":50972,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係未試過塞<br />\n但塞完出黎效果係幾唔好既情況下<br />\n點解仲一定要做返同一方式<br />\n如果效果好好就話做多幾獲無所謂姐<br />\n做完效果唔太好,仲死要做,做咩姐"},{"pid":"eedb1387520762a89220